7.11	We recommended that Management direct the Municipal Treasurer to:
Strictly implement the provisions of the Municipal Revenue Code in order to correct the assessment and collection of business taxes that will accrue to the Municipality;
Conduct verification on transactions recorded by the LGU and compare it to the amounts of sales declared in the application for renewal of business permits;
