11.9  	We recommended that Management:
Provide for the installation of secured compartments with cover to separate biodegradable from non-biodegradable waste in the garbage trucks, as well as truck cover during collection and transport of solid wastes;
Place the body number and telephone number of the LGU/office concerned on the visible parts of the truck used for collection and transport of solid wastes for identification and feedback mechanism from the constituents;
