Require the MENRO-Designate to efficiently handle the solid waste stored in the MRF to avoid the presence of flies and unpleasant odors which may pose health hazard in the area.

13.10 	We recommended that Management:
Conduct a thorough feasibility study in acquiring software in order to avoid incompatible application or difficulty in maintaining software. Also, consider the technical preparedness of the users in order to avoid unnecessary procurements;
Regularly maintain and update its assets especially their computer software which are prone to technical obsolescence;
See to it that all resources of the government be managed, expended or utilized efficiently and effectively in order to prevent loss or wastage.

